data.eml:eml: Synopsis of the Cochylini (Tortricidae: Tortricinae: Cochylini) of Iran, with the description of a new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Alipanah, Helen (2009): Synopsis of the Cochylini (Tortricidae: Tortricinae: Cochylini) of Iran, with the description of a new species. Zootaxa 2245: 1-31, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.190687
